SIMPLE: producer
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Producer
<hw>Pro*du"cer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>One who produces, brings forth, or
generates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who grows agricultural products, or manufactures
crude materials into articles of use.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Iron & Steel Manuf.)</fld> <def>A furnace for
producing combustible gas which is used for fuel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Produce race</ent>⟦br⟧
